  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nThe current default root-dir is `./.lodestar` in the current working directory when running `lodestar`.\r\nUsing a local root-dir has been convenient for development/debug purposes, but its not standard behavior for systemwide-installed programs.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nBrainstorm / implement a better default root-dir path. Some possible options:\r\n- $HOME/lodestar\r\n- Something following the XDG standard: https://specifications.freedesktop.org/basedir-spec/basedir-spec-latest.html#basics\r\n- ??\r\n",
